PRINTFORML 敵味方全員の武闘が気まぐれに変動！
FOR LOCAL, 0, BATTLE_COMMANDER_NUM:発動側
	IF RAND:2
		TIMES BATTLE_武闘パワー:発動側:LOCAL, 1.1
	ELSE
		TIMES BATTLE_武闘パワー:発動側:LOCAL, 0.9
	ENDIF
NEXT

